Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:17.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Attack with\NCannon. And end turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY] Argh, dang,\NKazuki, you're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:22.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, one more match!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna quit until\NI win at least one of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.86,Main,,0,0,0,,'Kay, but you realize that\Nmeans you're never goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:28.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY] Wise guy, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:31.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't believe we finally\Ncaught you without your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, you don't have\Nto say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A] Hey, guys?\NCan we play too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:40.87,Main,,0,0,0,,We got decks and all,\Nbut I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,The rules are kind of\Nhard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL B] You're good\Nat this. Right, Kazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:46.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:49.09,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, could\Nyou teach me a few tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] A WIXOSS party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's really just an excuse\Nfor people to play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:32.15,Main,,0,0,0,,When we did these before,\Nit was all guys, but lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:35.03,Main,,0,0,0,,a bunch of girls your age\Nhave been showing up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You three should come!\NOh come on, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:38.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Just sign up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and you should all\Nwear matching outfits!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:44.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That would be adorable!\NI could help out, if you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAN'S VOICE] Momoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:47.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You finally came by!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and you can still sign\Nup the day of the event,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:55.43,Main,,0,0,0,,so don't be afraid to\Nstop by and check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:58.51,Main,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:02:59.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[MOMOKA giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be done in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:01.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hang tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAN] Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:06.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:10.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry. What do you think?\NAre we in, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Participating as a\NSelector without having a wish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.78,Main,,0,0,0,,is more than just wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It's blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I'm going either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:28.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I might even find another\NSelector to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah... But my wish already--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. It already came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:37.43,Main,,0,0,0,,So if I won, it wouldn't\Nbe fair to the person I beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no need to\Nbe greedy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.81,Main,,0,0,0,,But if the other player isn't\Na Selector, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Meaning we're free to fight\Nall the dudes we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Good point! As long as\Nnobody's dreams are at stake,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:50.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely up\Nfor a battle or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:55.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure. That sounds okay.\NI suppose I'm on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,If nothing else, it's a chance\Nto try out my new deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Midoriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:03.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Midoriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE & RUKO giggle]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] So, ladies, I was\Nthinking about Momoka's idea
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.59,Main,,0,0,0,,for us to match our outfits.\NWe could be like a pop group!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] That's cute,\Nbut... kinda pricey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we spent\Ntoo much on cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:33.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Now that's more\Nin our price range!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not quite as fancy. But\Nwe can still match with these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Scrunchies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm! We might not\Nlook much like a pop group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.24,Main,,0,0,0,,But try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you gotta go with\Ngreen to match your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, cool,\NI found a red one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:51.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko's deck is white.\NHuh... No luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You can take this\Nweird-looking one instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't give me\Nthe icky one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:56.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] You're picking\Nugly ones on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Okay, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:03.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,we all bought these\Nmatching scrunchies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:08.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That's lovely! And I'm thrilled\Nthat you're making new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,But your hair is still\Nwet from your shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Your scrunchie is\Ngoing to mess it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine! So, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko almost got this\Nweird-looking one,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,but she ended up\Nwith aqua instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,even though her\Ndeck is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:22.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] All right, you\Ncan tell me all about it later,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,but first, go dry your hair,\Nand put something warmer on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You're going to\Ncatch your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw. It did get all messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeep! And the\Nscrunchie's all damp, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh. I'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO] Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it's best\Nif you get rid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:49.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--! Get rid of you? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO] Your wish\Nalready came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:54.81,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no need for\Nyou to battle anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure. But who\Ncares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:59.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I like you a whole\Nbunch, Midoriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I would never want\Nto get rid of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that if you keep me,\Nsomething might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Something terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Before I even met Ruko\Nand Yuzuki, you were my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko, and nothing\Nwill change that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:21.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:23.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I don't want to hear\Nyou talk like that ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:26.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Still need\Nto dry my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:33.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI grunts softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw! I suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:36.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I just can't get my hair\Ntied up right, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You are kind of clumsy\Nwith that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, let me get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.49,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Don't freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I'm not freaking out!\NI just need to learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:03.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Here, look! There's a\Nbig giraffe on the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:08.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Cool! Is it gonna\Nbattle the other giraffe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:12.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama. Not everything is\Nabout battles, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I am right.\NSo battle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Iona was\Nreally pretty, but, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,she was also kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama can beat\Nall the scaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:28.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[turnstile beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Looks like\NI'm here a bit early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:45.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I made it to the\Nmeeting spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.09,Main,,0,0,0,,And send.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] It's funny,\Nbut when I'm standing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:59.52,Main,,0,0,0,,in a big crowd like this. I\Nalmost feel like a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO] Come on, Hitoe,\Nyou are a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take your\Nword for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nice out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:14.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] When I first moved\Nto Tokyo, somehow, I felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.50,Main,,0,0,0,,there wasn't a sky here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks to all the\Nskyscrapers and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:23.88,Main,,0,0,0,,But there it is, as bright\Nand blue as it's ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,All this time, I never\Nnoticed. How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I just needed to look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:44.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Drop me! Throw me away now!\NPlease! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:49.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[train doors ding]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Ruko! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:51.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.37,Main,,0,0,0,,There were a whole bunch\Nof people in the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.95,Main,,0,0,0,,and the kid behind me was\Nabout to go in her pants,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,so I let her cut in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] We're making\NHitoe wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Huh. She\Nsaid she'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Too short! I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Guessing you came\Nup empty too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:14.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] She isn't answering\Nmy texts, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe she got mad at us\Nbecause we were late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't lose her temper\Nover something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Right? Back me up\Non this, Hanayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hanayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Somethin' goin' on, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a battlefield\Nsomewhere! Close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,--Not Hitoe...?\N--[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] They're strong.\NReally strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:50.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.97,Main,,0,0,0,,No. Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's my fault\Nyou're suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll try to end this\Nquickly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't need to win,\NI'll lose on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Please! You have\Nto keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:08.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Really. The only\Nwish I wanted already came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, neither one\Nof us have to go through
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:12.82,Main,,0,0,0,,these painful battles anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:16.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.24,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something important\NI haven't told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You know all about winning\Nand becoming an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.05,Main,,0,0,0,,--Sorry, mister!\N--[YUZUKI] Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:38.80,Main,,0,0,0,,However, you don't know\Nwhat it means to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:06.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[CROWD chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO & YUZUKI panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama. We close?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:12.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The battlefield\Nwent bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hanayo, do you\Nknow anything about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH] Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] There you are!\NYou had us all worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hitoe, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:45.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha-What do you want?\NHow do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.71,Main,,0,0,0,,If this is a joke,\NI don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.59,Main,,0,0,0,,--[HITOE whimpers]\N--[YUZUKI] Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hitoe. Tell\Nus what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:11.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Stand back!\NDon't touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoever you are,\Nleave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Hitoe... lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:21.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama is not sensing\Nher Selector power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.53,Main,,0,0,0,,She had a battle and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:27.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you saying she's\Nnot a Selector anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Did something messed\Nup happen to her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.21,Main,,0,0,0,,'cause she lost\Nher third battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.71,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hanayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:42.72,Main,,0,0,0,,After three losses, your\Nstatus as a Selector is revoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.31,Main,,0,0,0,,As for your wish,\Nit becomes corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] You mean like\Nyou get a curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:54.15,Main,,0,0,0,,For example, let's say your\Nwish was to become wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:57.15,Main,,0,0,0,,After losing three battles,\Nnot only would that wish
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:00.53,Main,,0,0,0,,fail to come true, you\Nwould plummet into poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:04.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] If your wish was\Nto be an expert pianist,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.91,Main,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't just lose your\Npiano. Something would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:11.12,Main,,0,0,0,,that would prevent you\Nfrom playing ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Something to ensure your\Nwish could never come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:16.84,Main,,0,0,0,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not really getting this.\NSo, what happened to Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.76,Main,,0,0,0,,All I can tell you is her\Nwish was to "make friends".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:27.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You can imagine what a\Ncorruption of that would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you're saying\Nshe lost her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Far worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:37.07,Main,,0,0,0,,She can never make\Nfriends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You saw what\Nstate she was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Seems if anyone has even the\Npotential to be her friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,her body goes through\Nsome sort of violent shock
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:47.79,Main,,0,0,0,,when they try to approach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.16,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:51.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Horrible, but\Nunfortunately, there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,With her third loss, not only\Nis her Selector status gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:58.00,Main,,0,0,0,,so are all her memories\Nrelated to those battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,as if they never\Neven took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What's happening? I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hitoe, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] How did they\Nknow me? Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] That didn't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Oh, God! Why?!\NWhy does this hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't! No! It hurts\Njust thinking about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Make it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.06,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll win and wish for Hitoe\Nto go back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I finally have a dream\Nworth fighting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't think of that! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though it didn't happen\Nas a result of winning battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,her wish did come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:08.78,Main,,0,0,0,,The corruption cannot be undone\Nby another Selector's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That's kind of an important\Ndetail you decided to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,secret from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it, why won't\Nyou say something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:23.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:26.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:30.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH cry]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:33.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah the sky would\Nget cloudy, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:41.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like rain soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I know I don't have\Nany right to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.99,Main,,0,0,0,,After ruining such\Nan innocent wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:50.03,Main,,0,0,0,,any fate I face\Nwill be too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I really did care\Nfor you, Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:07.51,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet, after this,\NI wish that we had
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.93,Main,,0,0,0,,never even met each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:38.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI cries softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I trusted you\Nall this time, Hanayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do.\NI'm afraid of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You can get rid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] It'll be easy.\NJust throw me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[knock on door]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Were you\Nfighting with Hanayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:08.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't wanna say it, but\Nyou've been acting weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You used to talk to\Nme about everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.54,Main,,0,0,0,,whether it was good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:20.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Not everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:23.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] If something's\Nbothering you, then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] You wouldn't say\Nthat if you knew the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:29.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] I mean, we've been\Ntogether our whole lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] What if\NI just told him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:36.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:40.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm fine.\NDon't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... You don't\Nwant to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:51.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. If you don't\Nneed me, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:54.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:55.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Hello? Oh, hey.\NReal good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:03.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, huh?\NAnd everyone is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.59,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that should be okay, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.59,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I'll be there. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:13.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:21.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I hate this.\NI hate this so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,This is really neat!\NWe've never been here before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:30.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess not. I usually only\Ncome to sit-down restaurants
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:32.11,Main,,0,0,0,,like this with\NGrandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] You're not going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:39.62,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I can't. Not yet. Whenever I\Nfail a test or hide something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,from Grandma, she\Nknows right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:46.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Tama, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh. I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:51.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything's all fuzzy\Nand white in Tama's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.30,Main,,0,0,0,,so I can't think at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,But I, I love battles!\NI know that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.01,Main,,0,0,0,,And I want more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:02.43,Main,,0,0,0,,And I don't like Ru sad...\NI don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Piriluk said a battle\Nhappened around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.11,Main,,0,0,0,,so I came to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured it might be\NYuzu-poo and the gals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.74,Main,,0,0,0,,so I sent a text\Nto her and Hitoe,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,to see what was\Nup, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzu-poo was too mean to reply,\Nbut Hitoe... Ha, ha. Well, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:21.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like she didn't even\Nknow who I was anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:24.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess she lost her third match\Nand got kicked to the curb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You've known all along\Nwhat happens to Selectors
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,and you never told anyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.84,Main,,0,0,0,,--What the heck?\N--Kids today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] C'mere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] ♪ Let's have\Na potty party! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:38.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] So funny story,\Nthe first time I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:40.76,Main,,0,0,0,,a Selector battle, it wasn't\Neven mine. It was Iona's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:45.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] On my way out from a\Nphoto shoot, I guess she was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,picking a fight with\Nsome other Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:49.86,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause I got pulled into\Ntheir field out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.90,Main,,0,0,0,,She could have warned me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Anyhoo, her opponent\Nhad already lost two battles
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,and was at the\Nend of her rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.45,Main,,0,0,0,,She was all like, huffing\Nand puffing and just,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.99,Main,,0,0,0,,super-sick looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I could tell she wanted\Nto win real bad though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Well, Iona\Ndidn't give a crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Long story short, there\Nwas a lot of thrashing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,and not much in the\Nway of happy endings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] When it was over,\Nshe must've had a stroke
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,or something. It was bad.\NLike, ambulance and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you heard, but\NIona's LRIG is super sadistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.98,Main,,0,0,0,,That poor girl didn't\Nstand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] D-do you know\Nwhat happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:30.81,Main,,0,0,0,,None of my business, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, I saw that she got\Ntaken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:35.44,Main,,0,0,0,,But she was looking pretty bad,\Nso it's tough to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:37.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] No, that's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I know, like,\Nfor serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Compared to something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh, not being able to make\Nfriends isn't so bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.16,Main,,0,0,0,,H-how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You forgot already? When we\Nfought, I did that awesome thing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,where I could\Nsee her wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, she wasn't exactly\NMiss Popularity to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:58.47,Main,,0,0,0,,So, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.55,Main,,0,0,0,,This is kind of a\Nplus for you, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:03.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Now you don't have to humor\Nthe poor disaster anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:05.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanging around her wasn't\Ndoing you any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, seriously,\Nshe was super frumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.89,Main,,0,0,0,,At least now she knows\Nnobody will be her friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:12.86,Main,,0,0,0,,so she doesn't have to latch\Nonto people like a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:14.82,Main,,0,0,0,,So yeah. Even if she\Ndoesn't make friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.28,Main,,0,0,0,,it's pretty much better\Nfor everyone that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.15,Main,,0,0,0,,That's really what\Nyou think, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.\NSo anyhow I--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You take that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Not gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:32.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen up! You take it back,\Nor I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow. I am, like,\Nreally scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You must think super\Nhighly of yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:41.22,Main,,0,0,0,,"I can't live if Ru-Ru\Nwon't forgive me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, if you\Ntruly can't forgive me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.56,Main,,0,0,0,,why don't we have a battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you\Nbeat me bad enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:54.81,Main,,0,0,0,,maybe I'll cry and see the\Nerror of my wicked old ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:55.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Yeah, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:56.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] We can battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:22:01.90,Main,,0,0,0,,And after I beat you,\Nwe're going to visit Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:04.62,Main,,0,0,0,,So you can tell my friend\Nthat you're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hitoe lost three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.17,0:23:44.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] That is, like,\Nso messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:46.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Do you\Nthink I'm stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:48.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] No! No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] What's\Nit matter to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.85,0:23:53.10,Main,,0,0,0,,This Pure Heart.
